div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="3" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1659672791687" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1659672791687"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>03</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="3" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659672791727" class="element-wrap" data-id="1659672791727"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>Cover mixture with plastic wrap (touching the&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">surface). Cool to room temperature and then place&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">in the fridge overnight.</span></p></div></div></div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="4" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1659672811063" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1659672811063"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>04</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="4" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1659672811148" class="element-wrap" data-id="1659672811148"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>When ready to decorate the Pavlovas, whisk the&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">chocolate mixture on medium-high until fluffy.</span></p></div></div></div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="5" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1666581448270" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1666581448270"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>05</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="5" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1666581448221" class="element-wrap" data-id="1666581448221"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>Add the remaining cream and continue to whisk&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">until stiff.</span></p></div></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1669937144479" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1669937144479" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Pavlovas</h1></div></div><div data-label="Icon List" data-key="icon-list" id="m-1669937141371" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-iconlist" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1669937141371" style="display: block;"><div class="module gf_module-left gf_module-left-lg gf_module--md gf_module--sm gf_module--xs "><ul class="gf_icon-list"><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="1" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1669937141351" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1669937141351"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>01</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="1" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1669937141371-2" class="element-wrap" data-id="1669937141371-2"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>Preheat oven to 120°C/110 Fan/250°F.</p></div></div></div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="2" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1669937141383" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1669937141383"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>02</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="2" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1669937141363" class="element-wrap" data-id="1669937141363"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>Line 2 baking trays with baking paper -use a little of&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">the pavlova mixture to "glue" the corners down.</span></p></div></div></div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="3" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1669937141422" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1669937141422"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>03</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="3" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1669937141466" class="element-wrap" data-id="1669937141466"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>In the bowl of a stand mixer, whisk the egg whites&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">and cream of tartar on medium speed until it forms</span></p><p>soft peaks.</p></div></div></div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="4" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1669937141421" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1669937141421"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>04</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="4" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1669937141369" class="element-wrap" data-id="1669937141369"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>Gradually add the sugar, one tablespoon at a time,&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">whisking for 30 seconds between additions.</span></p></div></div></div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="5" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1669937141385" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1669937141385"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>05</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="5" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1669937141282" class="element-wrap" data-id="1669937141282"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>Using a large ice cream scoop, place 2 scoops onto&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">the baking sheet, repeating to make 10 pavlovas (5</span></p><p>per tray).</p></div></div></div></li><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="6" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1669937404230" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1669937404230"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>05</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="6" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1669937404341" class="element-wrap" data-id="1669937404341"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>Use an offset spatula or butter knife to push down&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">lightly, then smooth to form pavlovas into circles.</span></p><p>Using the offset spatula, swipe up diagonally to&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">form grooves.</span></p></div></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1669937443708" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1669937443708" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">To Decorate</h1></div></div><div data-label="Icon List" data-key="icon-list" id="m-1669937467347" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-iconlist" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1669937467347" style="display: block;"><div class="module gf_module-left gf_module-left-lg gf_module--md gf_module--sm gf_module--xs "><ul class="gf_icon-list"><li style="margin-bottom: 10px"><span class="gf-il-icon item-content" data-index="1" data-key="content" style="width: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1669937467358" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1669937467358"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>01</p></div></div></span><div class="gf-il-content item-content" data-index="1" data-key="content1" style="padding-left: 45px"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1669937467347-2" class="element-wrap" data-id="1669937467347-2"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p>Just before serving, dollop the White Chocolate&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.4px; text-align: inherit;">Cream onto the Pavlova